{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They took you away and you were finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got some kind of a sickness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was dysentery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what it is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is-- you went out with blood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's a very catchy sickness, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, you have to be quarantined because other people would get sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Myself and another boy got sick on this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first, I was afraid to report it because I knew, in Rabka, if you sick, that's-- that's the end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- eventually, I had to go to the doctor because I was getting very weak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was not a doctor, it was a guy who was a male nurse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he saw what it is, he says he reported it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the two of us, when they were going to work, we had to go separate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us on a truck and they brought us to the ghetto in Krakow to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That friend of mine who had the same sickness, the next day he died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a little bit older than I am.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was-- I was unconscious maybe for two days, and I came back to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And would you believe it, that they brought me back to Rabka from Pla-- from the ghetto, from the hospital?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I heard that two or three days later, they liquidated the ghetto and they killed all the sick people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was feeling somebody was watching over me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in-- and in Plaszow, I was holding on as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they needed a group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schindler was already having his own factory in the-- in the Zablocie, Deutsche Emailwarenfabrik.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got it by Schindler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got it in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
